			  			<HR color=#000000 SIZE=-1>
			  			i have been playing archspace for a couple of weeks now and have been attacked by about 4 different people now.  I have noticed that most players send a small fleet first to find out enemy strength then in the second attack send a lager force.  I think it would be cool if you could have more than one defence plan and you could assign defense plans to different sizes of attacks.  For example, i could have a defense plan for when someone attacks me with fewer than 5 ships, and a defense plan for attacks with more than 5 ships.  I think this would also encourage players to be more cautious when attacking other players as they wont know exactly how many enemies they are facing just from sending a scout force.  I think players should at least have the option of more defense plans.  But maybe to even it out if you use a ship in one defense plan, you cant use it in another.  So if a defender has dooms in the first defense wave as compared to destroyers or something, you know they probably have a much larger second defense plan 						<P align=right> </P>
					</TD>
